article.description: The Big 12, Conference contest between No. 10 Oklahoma State and
article.headline: The Big 12, Conference contest between No. 10 Oklahoma State and
article.linkText: The Big 12, Conference contest between No. 10 Oklahoma State and
article.story:
LINCOLN, Nebraska (Ticker) -- Icy conditions have grounded 
Oklahoma State.

The Big 12 Conference contest between No. 10 Oklahoma State and
Nebraska was postponed on Saturday, as the Cowboys were unable
to fly due to the ice storm that blanketed the Oklahoma City
area.

No makeup date has yet been announced by the Big 12.

Originally scheduled for 1:30 p.m. EST, the contest was moved
back until 8:00 p.m. before eventually being called off.
